TEXT.S: Nansiku i Pingtung a kuwan nu Kalinku ku niyazu' nu Nansiku. u kasalumaluma' nu Nansiku sa, 123 ku luma'. kumud nu kasabinawlan sa, 401 ku tademawan. kasabinawlan nu Ingcumin sa, 390 ku tademaw, pakalatu 97%. u zuma sa, cay ku Ingcumin, 11 ku tademaw, pakalatu 3%. u kasabinacadan, Paiwan94%, zumazuma2%.
